  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered human of middle years, with brown eyes set beneath heavy lids and a square, work-worn jaw. Black hair is kept in a plain, close-cropped arrangement that emphasizes a strong brow and a thick neck. Bronze skin bears the ingrained marks of long hours in heated, smoky interiors, with fine creases at the eyes and mouth. The hands are large and callused, with short, uneven nails typical of constant handling of glass and casks.",
